title: Orson Scott Card - Latest Ender Novel Collection (epub)
description:
A collection of Orson Scott Card's Ender sci-fi novels. Arranged not according to publication date but in chronological timeline.

Book 1 - Earth Unaware
Book 2 - Earth Afire
Book 3 - "Not published yet"
Book 4 - Enders Game
Book 5 - Enders Shadow
Book 6 - A War of Gifts An Ender Story
Book 7 - Shadow of the Hegemon
Book 8 - Shadow Puppets
Book 9 - Shadow of the Giant
Book 10 - Ender in Exile
Book 11 - Shadows in Flight
Book 12 - Speaker for the Dead
Book 13 - Xenocide
Book 14 - Children of the Mind
Book 15 - "Not published yet"

*Doesn't include side story or companion story.
